cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI 

This paper discusses the application of deep learning to search ranking, which is a problem in information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the architecture of a neural network, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses bias and cold start, which are topics in natural language processing (cs.CL) and recommender systems (cs.IR).
